title: Steele eager to get started, and it showed at Silverado
text:
> Sports Steele eager to get started, and it showed at Silverado Brendan Steele walks up the third fairway of the Silverado Resort North Course with vineyards in the background during the first round of the Frys.com PGA Tour golf tournament Thursday, Oct. 15, 2015, in Napa, Calif. Steele shot a 9-under-par 63. (AP Photo/Eric Risberg) The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
